headline.main: Israel: Palestinian Militant Killed in Shootout
headline.print_headline: Israel: Palestinian Militant Killed in Shootout

lead_paragraph: Demand for travel to the United States over the coming months has flattened out following a positive start to the year, with uncertainty over a possible new travel order likely deterring visitors, travel analysis company ForwardKeys said on Monday.
